name: WALKING KIKI LISTENING TO REMI WOLF X POLO & PAN
description:
I sometimes get nervous being outside so when I walk Kiki I always have headphones on. Today I listened to a Remi Wolf POLO and PAN remix which made my surrounds take on this pop art vibe which was a great distraction and made the walk super fun.

Personal daily art story
Number 9 #STOREEZ by Cat Brown/ Treasvre Trove
